<div id='countdown'>
  <%= image_tag "leafs", class: "leafs left" %>
  <%= image_tag "leafs", class: "leafs right" %>
  <h1 class="text-center counter-text">Banquet Invitation</h1>
  <div class="countdown-container">
      <div class="countdown-el days-c">
          <p class="big-text" id="days">0</p>
          <span class='counter-text'>DAYS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="countdown-el hours-c">
          <p class="big-text" id="hours">0</p>
          <span class='counter-text'>HOURS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="countdown-el mins-c">
          <p class="big-text" id="mins">0</p>
          <span class='counter-text'>MINS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="countdown-el seconds-c">
          <p class="big-text" id="seconds">0</p>
          <span class='counter-text'>SECONDS</span>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <%= image_tag "wine.jpg", class: 'wine' %>
    <p>欢迎我的小狮子 🦁🦁 参加我们的520晚宴!</p>
    <p>当天晚上,</p>
    <p>将会由主业女仆人妻</p>
    <p>兼职<b>"Chief"</b>的花花为您烹饪</p>
    <p>希望能为您带来一个难忘的晚上 🍻🍻</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <p class="counter-text text-left">日期: 2022/05/20</p>
    <p class="counter-text text-left">着装: 穿什么都好看</p>
    <p class="counter-text text-left">地址:  我们家</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p class="sub-title text-left">Menu 🌮</p>

  <div class="dish-container">
      <%= image_tag "salad.jpg", class: 'dish' %>
      <div>
        <p class="">🥗 头盘 🥗</p>
        <p>千岛酱蔬菜沙拉</p>
        <p class='en'>Green Salad With Homemade Thousand Island Dressing</p>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dish-container">
    <%= image_tag "Scallops.webp", class: 'dish' %>
    <div>
      <p class="">🍤 副菜 🍤</p>
      <p>蒜香黄油煎扇贝</p>
      <p class='en'>Lemon Garlic Butter Scallops</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dish-container">
    <%= image_tag "sirloin.jpg", class: 'dish' %>
    <div>
      <p class="">🥩 主菜 🥩</p>
      <p>低温慢煮西冷牛排</p>
      <p class='en'>Sous vide Sirloin Steak</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dish-container">
    <%= image_tag "whisky-sour.webp", class: 'dish' %>
    <div>
      <p class="">🍹 酒水 🍹</p>
      <p>鸡尾酒</p>
      <p class='en'>Homemade Cocktail Drink</p>
    </div>
  </div>
    <div class="dish-container">
    <%= image_tag "flower.jpg", class: 'dish' %>
    <div>
      <p class="">💕❤️ 神秘正餐 ❤️💕</p>
      <p>花花公主</p>
      <p class='en'>Princesses</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center counter-text sign-text" id="darwing-canvas">
      <div class="text-left sub-title" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">签收</div>
      <canvas class="drawing" id="sign"></canvas>
      <button class="message-btn button-27" style="margin-top: 20px;">💌<</button>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.message-btn {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
}

/* CSS */
